{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"language"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"language","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sending notifications in a specific language","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Language-based segmentation"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Supporting in-app language switching"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard."}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Support in-app language selection:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"setLanguage:","roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications."}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setLanguage:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications."}],